 83→ * @param folderKey - Decrypted AES-256 key for this folder
 84→ * @param ipnsPrivateKey - Decrypted Ed25519 private key for IPNS
 85→ * @param ipnsName - IPNS name for this folder
 86→ * @param parentId - Parent folder ID (null for root)
 87→ * @param name - Display name for this folder
