  1→/**
  2→ * CipherBox Desktop - Webview Entry Point
  3→ *
  4→ * On app start:
  5→ * 1. Check for --dev-key mode (debug builds skip Core Kit entirely)
  6→ * 2. Try silent refresh from Keychain-stored refresh token
  7→ * 3. Initialize Core Kit and show CipherBox-branded login UI
  8→ * 4. After auth completes, the Rust side has all keys -- app transitions to
  9→ *    headless menu bar mode (webview window hides)
 10→ *
 11→ * The webview is only used for the auth flow. Once authenticated,
 12→ * the app runs as a menu bar utility with FUSE mount.
 13→ */
 14→
